<p>话少，钱多，还爱猫。</p>
<p>我想嫁我想嫁我想嫁！</p>
<p><img src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180407/c6c3979a90c1411799ca1d70f0f277a3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
